[{"Timecode":"","Caption":"{QTtext}{width:960}{textColor:65280,65280,65280}{justify:center}{timescale:1000}{backColor:0,0,0}{plain}{font:Verdana}{size:20}\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:01.030]","Caption":"\nHere's a difficult truth, a lot of folks\nthink they're being\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:03.830]","Caption":"\na leader when, in fact, they're closer to\nan overbearing control freak.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:07.580]","Caption":"\nThe classic micro-manager, it's very\ncommon.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:09.611]","Caption":"\nYou're an over achiever who knows how to\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:11.625]","Caption":"\nget things done, so when you're promoted\ninto leadership\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:14.530]","Caption":"\nyou feel compelled to hover over your\nemployees\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:16.760]","Caption":"\nto be sure their work meets your high\nstandards.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:19.390]","Caption":"\nBut now you've been warned micro-managing\nwill rapidly\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:22.800]","Caption":"\nhurt rapport and team culture Whether you\nintended\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:26.270]","Caption":"\nto send negative signals or not, that's\nexactly what micro-managing does.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:30.100]","Caption":"\nIt tells your employees you don't trust\nthem, they're not competent, and without\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:36.160]","Caption":"\nyou looking over their shoulder, you think\nthey're likely to mess things up.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:40.110]","Caption":"\nThese are not the kinds of messages you\nwish to send.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:42.990]","Caption":"\nI'd like you to remember that your job is\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:44.650]","Caption":"\nto focus on the outcomes more than the\nprocess.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:47.430]","Caption":"\nYou focus on the what and strive to let\nthem focus on the how.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:52.190]","Caption":"\nYou can make that happen by following\nthese three steps.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:00:55.489]","Caption":"\nFirst, spend time carefully clarifying\ninstructions and expectations up front.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:01.120]","Caption":"\nThe more effectively you assign tasks from\nthe beginning,\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:03.850]","Caption":"\nthe less you deem to feel compelled to\nmicromanage.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:06.560]","Caption":"\nAnd be sure to ask questions to\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:08.820]","Caption":"\nverify that they clearly understand your\nexpectation.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:12.375]","Caption":"\nNext, make a deal with yourself concerning\nhow long you will wait before giving\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:17.280]","Caption":"\nin to the desire to checkup on your\nemployee's progress.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:20.490]","Caption":"\nHere's a great goal.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:21.700]","Caption":"\nResist checking in until at least 60 to\n70% of the allotted time has passed.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:27.290]","Caption":"\nNot only do you need that time to focus on\nyour own work, but\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:30.420]","Caption":"\nthis tactic will also clearly signal to\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:32.540]","Caption":"\nyour employee exactly how much you trust\nthem.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:35.175]","Caption":"\nFinally, once you do call or stop by, I\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:38.600]","Caption":"\nwant you to change the nature of your\ncheck-ins.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:41.220]","Caption":"\nThat's right.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:41.660]","Caption":"\nNot only do I\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:42.280]","Caption":"\nwant you to check in fewer times, but\ndifferently as well.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:45.820]","Caption":"\nInstead of saying, let me see the work or\nis it\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:48.760]","Caption":"\ndone yet, make the choice to be helpful\ninstead of simply evaluative.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:53.790]","Caption":"\nFor example, ask, are you good?\nAre you on track?\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:56.840]","Caption":"\nOr, is there anything I can help you with?\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:01:59.530]","Caption":"\nThe perfectionist in you will sometimes\nwant to over-control certain situations.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:02:04.010]","Caption":"\nEven though your expertise is very useful\nto your employees,\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:02:07.730]","Caption":"\nit turns out, giving them a little more\nspace and autonomy.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:02:10.635]","Caption":"\nIt makes them feel competent and\nconfident,\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:02:13.260]","Caption":"\nwhich increases the quality of their work.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:02:16.060]","Caption":"\nLet go a little bit more and you might be\nsurprised at the work they produce.\n\n"},{"Timecode":"[00:02:19.970]","Caption":"\n\n"}]